      "message": "Done.\n\n(On the observation and discussion...)\n\nI agree, the plan you gave would be best possible. I\u0027d suggest a full-width-pid, if 4 redundant bytes isn\u0027t too big a price to pay... it feels like an unnecessary optimization. However, yes, the utility of doing this is marginal and probably not worth it.",
